{
  "texts": [
    "Audit trails record the manifest of the application when it is launched.",
    "Manifests show how applications are permitted to communicate.",
    "Citizens can use them to verify that raw video footage is sanitized for privacy before being consumed by downstream applications.The key challenge, however, is to provide a basis for the citizen to establish trust in the integrity of the audit trail presented by a delivery drone.",
    "In Privadome, we address this problem by requiring delivery drones to be equipped with trusted hardware.",
    "We use the ARM TrustZone [10] in our experimental prototype, but any similar attestation hardware should suffice."
  ]
}